  "Description": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>LOG CORRUPT <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> RECOVERING DAMAGED SECTORS<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>\"the captain ::: gone<br>tried to wake them for their watch<br>no sign of them ::: nothing on the cameras<br>door logs are normal, no kit missing<br>where are they?<br>where are we\"<>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span>日志损坏<span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span>正在恢复损坏扇区<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>“船长:::消失了<br>想把它叫醒，让它起来值班<br>但没有任何迹象:::监控里什么也没看到<br>门禁记录正常，装备无缺失<br>它在哪儿？<br>我们在哪儿？'<>",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span> 日誌毀損 <span class=\"name name-img\">CLOCK</span> 正在復原受損區塊 <span class=\"name name-img\">SLASH</span><br><br><VAL_ON>「船長:::走了<br>試圖叫醒大家換班守夜<br>找不到人:::攝影機裡什麼都沒拍到<br>出入日誌正常，未缺少裝備<br>大家人在哪裡？<br>我們在哪裡」<>"
  },
